body:
What? What I meant by that was that there are so many posts being yanked to guilds like +communism101 and so few users unyanking their posts from there that the majority of the posts in +general that are less than a month old are going to come from the same few users.

<sup> - sfrohne [If you're going to post a screenshot of this comment, **don't** censor my username]</sup>
